    <h1>Mar 16 2026: Hello World!</h1>
    <hr>
    <p> Fixed my messed up GitHub repo by
        rebasing to "main" branch and deleting "master" branch.
        I also installed npm on my laptop (in which will become
        my main device to work from) and installed "live-server"
        addon. This fixed an issue I encountered with Webstorm
        incorrectly hosting my webpage which led to a 404 error
        when accessing my navbar. live-server allows me to work
        on my website without issue. I am also adding my first
        entry to my devlog (hello). Hopefully this will be the
        first of many. Later this week, my SSD should be here so
        I can boot and use my server FINALLY! My wife is unaware
        this is happening and will be pleasantly surprised when I
        host a Minecraft server with her favorite mods installed.
        Thank you for reading my first devlog. Goodbye for now.
    </p>
